ygData.messageBody:
Okay, so far I have 8 people who submitted names of their characters to me. If you people ever
want to form a guild, we need the names of 3 more people (Alex in guild liao).

Other wise, we just act as an unofficial group. So far, we have 1 decently balance grouping.

Garren(Tank, Secondary Healer), Leshrec(Magic Support) and Yiyang(Tank). One more healer and this
group can be off to run around in Upper Guk(Just don't go too deep).

Don't go to High hold yet. It is still a tad too dangerous for you.
